# 🚀 eBay Product Data Pipeline (Automation System)

## 📌 Overview

This project is an automated data pipeline that extracts product data from eBay, processes and cleans the data, and outputs a structured CSV file ready for business use.

The goal is not just scraping — but building a reliable system that produces clean, usable datasets for e-commerce workflows, analysis, and automation.

---

## ⚙️ Features

✔ Extract product data from eBay search pages
✔ Handles dynamic content using Playwright
✔ Filters out ads, invalid listings, and noise
✔ Cleans and normalizes data (price, duplicates, formatting)
✔ Adds basic category tagging
✔ Outputs structured CSV file (ready for use)

